name: Amazon Warriors World
description: The 1 stage of NFT collection "Amazon Warriors World" is a digital art collection with images of legendary female warriors from various cultures. Each NFT represents a specific warrior with a unique history, appearance, and set of skills. The collection is inspired by the history and mythology of the Amazon warrior women. Each NFT is a one-of-a-kind digital asset stored in the Bitcoin blockchain, which makes it authentic and unique. The collection celebrates female strength, courage, and resilience and pays tribute to the legendary warriors who have inspired generations. Every woman is an Amazon at heart.
